        "timestamp": "2019-06-17 07:46:10.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nHi, similarly to this change: https://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/sdnc/oam/+/89762/\n\nI only moved the npm install to the right place. If this change breaks something for you then pls let me know or take over. In any case npm install should not be executed on the every and each start of the container - we know the dependencies beforehand (package.json is part of the repo).\n\nI am aware that node-RED project (on which this component is based on) can run npm install during its runtime - but that hugely depends on the use-case.\n\nThanks",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
